    "summary": "The user describes symptoms of heat exposure combined with neurological deficits (slurred speech, confusion, heaviness in tongue). The assistant repeatedly identifies these as potential \"red flags\" and correctly advises the user to seek medical attention rather than just sleeping it off or using home remedies.",
